Playing multiple sports allows you to not only develop into a well-rounded athlete, but also a well-rounded individual. https://t.co/W9C8ABL2Rw

You add Davante Adams, Chandler Jones and pay your cornerstone guys with a Super Bowl in mind. 

In the AFC West, you’re going for it all, or you’re going to get lapped. 

That’s it. 

Progress is good, but the team is built to win now. You know what the goal is.

A lot of us labeled the last few #Raiders seasons as the “No Excuse” years.

I’ll just say 2022 is the “Get It Done” year.

No team is perfect, so there will always be “excuses” or built-in reasons that a squad came up short.

Regardless, gotta get the job (winning) done though.
